'''Empathy'''，是一个[[即时通讯客户端|即时通讯客户端]]軟體，支持文本、音頻、視頻及多种通讯协议。

Empathy 同时提供了可重复利用的[[图形界面|图形界面]]及[[图形工具箱|图形工具箱]]，以开发[[GNOME|GNOME]]上的同类软件<ref>{{cite news
 | url = http://arstechnica.com/open-source/news/2007/08/empathy-toolkit-simplifies-instant-messaging-integration.ars
 | title = Empathy toolkit simplifies instant messaging integration
 | last = Paul
 | first = Ryan
 | date = 25 August 2007
 | work = [[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]
 | accessdate = 20 March 2010
 | archive-date = 2011-06-06
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110606142241/http://arstechnica.com/open-source/news/2007/08/empathy-toolkit-simplifies-instant-messaging-integration.ars
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>，构架基于[[Telepathy|Telepathy]]框架。

2.24版本之后，Empathy纳入GNOME桌面项目，<ref>{{cite news
 | url = http://arstechnica.com/open-source/reviews/2009/03/hands-on-gnome-226-brings-incremental-improvement.ars
 | title = Hands-on: GNOME 2.26 brings incremental improvements
